des:
Call yourself a movie fan? Take this quiz to find out how well you know about the India film industry. The is skill is quiz game which will ask 5 questions answer it and improve your knowledge about the film industry. The questions are based on the knowledge of all series and it will be updated with all the categories. It will make you love and play it all the time. The skill is all about the knowledge increasing domain with a lovable and happy manner.

The skill will be updated monthly with all new questions such that all customers can use this skill for fun and knowledge.
